hnologies: ZoomX foam, a sculpted Air Zoom unit and ReactX foam. It s the most responsive Pegasus ever, providing high energy return unlike any other. With a lighter-than-air upper, it decreases weight and increases breathability so you can fly faster.','https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/4b476e07-8dce-4d55-8ff7-49299ab0696f/NIKE+PEGASUS+PREMIUM.png','HIGH','Running',4.3),(48,'Nike Pegasus 41 By You',729.90,'Responsive cushioning in the Pegasus provides an energised ride for everyday road running. Experience lighter-weight energy return with dual Air Zoom units and a ReactX foam midsole. Plus, an improved engineered mesh on the upper decreases weight and increases breathability. With bold and bright colours to choose from and a trio of performance alternatives, this shoe is prepared for your special touch.','https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_864_v1/f_auto,b_rgb:f5f5f5/2e4b0872-a990-4df9-a2ee-17e27aa4d65c/custom-nike-air-zoom-pegasus-41-shoes-by-you.png','LOW','Running',4.8),(49,'Nike Air Monarch IV',329.90,'Nike Air Monarch IV sets you up for working out with durable leather on top for support. Lightweight foam teams up with Nike Air cushioning for comfort in every stride.','https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/f9a8deaa-87f2-4191-92b8-c7661aae48de/AIR+MONARCH+IV.png','MID','Running',4.1),(50,'Nike Mercurial Superfly 10 Elite',1179.90,'Obsessed with speed? So are the game s biggest stars. That s why we made this Elite boot with an improved 3/4-length Air Zoom unit. It gives you and the sport s fastest players the propulsive feel needed to break through the back line. The result is the most responsive Mercurial we ve ever made, because you demand greatness from yourself and your footwear.','https://static.nike.com/a/images/t_PDP_1728_v1/f_auto,q_auto:eco/2d380ad3-1519-4457-87bb-ef1f88facfe8/ZM+SUPERFLY+10+ELITE+FG.png ','HIGH','Football',3.6);
